## **📖 Practical Steps for Effective Goal-Setting**

1️⃣ **Define Your Why** – Clarify the purpose behind your goal.  
2️⃣ **Make it Specific & Time-Bound** – Avoid vague aspirations.  
3️⃣ **Break it Down into Micro-Tasks** – Small steps lead to big achievements.  
4️⃣ **Use Accountability Systems** – Social commitment improves success rates.  
5️⃣ **Adapt & Iterate** – Regularly adjust goals based on progress & feedback.

